version_description: Getting ready for something huge!  Be on the lookout for brand new features, additional bug fixes and improvements coming soon!

· Checkout and purchase your shoes within the app!
· Improved DSW Rewards experience with points progress and points history
· Manage your account and view past purchases
· Create a Rewards account to earn points towards certificates
· Manage and share your Favorites list
· Browse our full selection of shoes
· Added filter and sort functionality
· Need it Today filter for shoes in 4 hours
· Improved store locator
· Speak with a DSW associate with Live Chat

· Crash and bug fixes
· Checkout and purchase with PayPal
· View posts from social media on the product page for style inspiration

· Add to your Favorites list without being logged in
· Additional how-to-wear features in a collection page
· Bug fixes

· iPad native support
· Ability to manage an anonymous profile
· Copy and paste your offers straight from the app
· Easily find shoes in your store with improved store pick up information
· Bug fixes

· Find your best fit with TrueFit and know you’re getting the right size, every time.
· Receive notifications and never miss a deal again
· Shopping on the web? When you tap a link from the web, we’ll now open the app to the correct screen
· Updates to the product page and shopping bag for a better in store experience
· Updates to product scan to help you easily find shoes when in the store
· Search for a store using the map app of your choice
· Bug fixes

* Optimized for iPhone X and Face ID
* New iMessage app to easily share Favorites, Recently Viewed and your Shopping Bag with your friends straight from your messages
* Share a single shoe from the product page to anyone in your contacts list for fast feedback
* Simplified way to copy a promo code for all of the best deals
* Updated product scan to make it easier to find the shoe you want while shopping in store
* Bug Fixes

[+] Optimized for iOS 11 and the iPhone X
[+] Supports FaceID to log in and to make changes to your account

[+] Added search functionality to filters to make it easier to search for the brands you love
[+] Simplified way to get back to the item you were viewing directly from the shopping bag
[+] Made it easier to view offers by adding pinch to zoom
[+] Improved loading on the homepage so you can get to your shoes faster
[+] Bug fixes

[+] Improved offer messaging so you know exactly what you’re getting
[+] Bug fixes and other optimizations

[+] Saving your points for bigger Rewards? We’ll let you know when you have enough points to get a Reward sooner with our new Rewards Now functionality.
[+] Donate your unused Reward to charity and give back to someone in need.
[+] Easily shop for your family and friends by filling out a profile for those you shop for the most.
[+] Vote for your favorite shoes.

[+] Improvements to the checkout for a more streamlined experience
[+] Optimized for iOS 12
[+] Bug fixes

[+] Updated Forgot Password flow to help you get into your account faster and easier
[+] Homepage improvements for a better shopping experience
[+] Bug fixes

[+] Get notified when you’re near a store and have a Reward available!
[+] Bug fixes and improvements

[+] Search for shoes using your voice!
[+] Updated Clearance Calculator to make it easier to figure out your savings in store
[+] Bug fixes

[+] We've launched Afterpay - Buy now. Pay later. Get your items delivered now and pay in four installment every 2 weeks, interest free
[+] Made it even easier to write a review for your favorite pair of shoes
[+] Cleaned up some bugs and performance issues to make your shopping experience even better

[+] Performance improvements and bug fixes

[+] Want to know which DSW exclusive brand you are? Update your app to take the quiz.
[+] Your rewards, your way! This update includes new VIP features; MyPerk and the ability to add your VIP Loyalty card to your Apple Wallet.

[+] Never miss a deal again! Opt-in for email offers at check out!
[+] Performance enhancements and bug fixes

[+] Love those shoes? Pay how you want! Now offering even more ways to checkout using ApplePay and Venmo.
[+] Never miss a deal again! Opt-in at check out to receive offers via text!
[+] Need to find that shoe at a DSW near you? Select 'Pick Up In-Store' and check every DSW near (or far) in one easy list!

[+] Found that pair and need to get it ordered faster than you can say Shoe Lover?! Use the new QuickAdd feature to get them to your cart in record time!
[+] Performance enhancements and bug fixes

[+] Love using our app in the store to get all the details on your new favorite pair of shoes? Use our barcode scanner to get a whole new view on that shoe.
[+] Performance enhancements and bug fixes

[+] Pumpkin Spice Lattes aren't the only exciting thing this fall! Are you Kelly & Katie, Mix No. 6 or maybe Bleecker and Bond? Discover which of DSW's exclusive brands you are by taking the newly re-designed for fall exclusives quiz!
